import React from "react"

import { Container, Typography, Card, Grid } from "@material-ui/core"
export default () => {

	return (
		<Container>

			<Card>
				<Grid container>
					<Grid>
						<Typography>Bienvenido</Typography>
					</Grid>
				</Grid>
			</Card>

		</Container>


	)
}
